# 🏧 Roro's ATM Simulator  

![ATM GIF](https://media.giphy.com/media/3oEjI6SIIHBdRxXI40/giphy.gif)  

A simple **C++ console-based ATM program** that allows you to check balance, withdraw, and deposit money. Built as a beginner-friendly project to practice functions, loops, and conditionals in C++.  

---

## ✨ Features
✅ Check account balance  
✅ Withdraw money (with insufficient balance check)  
✅ Deposit money  
✅ User-friendly menu system  
✅ Loop to perform multiple transactions  

